{"tid":2137886,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"推測定罪 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T10:46:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8db45c4e5016f90785c324d7a3be2e8eec3fa782","tid":2137886,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/H63PQDNZABBVJLPBZTHVCFB7XU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FH63PQDNZABBVJLPBZTHVCFB7XU%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=5c7119c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FH63PQDNZABBVJLPBZTHVCFB7XU%2F&h=d049b17c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/H63PQDNZABBVJLPBZTHVCFB7XU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n推測定罪 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/36TVP_C-zrrxQgs6X_roZ4MjO2c=/715x530/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JSTJLMBNXVB3PNMSAQO3SEFRFI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F36TVP_C-zrrxQgs6X_roZ4MjO2c%3D%2F715x530%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJSTJLMBNXVB3PNMSAQO3SEFRFI.png&h=61b72046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。裁判官指出，「辣椒油主要會令皮膚和眼睛有灼熱感覺，但不會帶來後遺症，罪責較輕。惟棒球棍若用來向頭部揮擊，可令傷者成植物人，即使向身體施襲，也可造成骨折甚至永久傷殘。故以18個月作量刑起點，沒有任何減刑因素。」<br />\n<br />\n我坐在車上看這段新聞，然後下車，打開自己的車尾箱，望望裏面的東西，假設置身香港，遇到香港警察，不知會有甚麼下場？車上有一箱水，假設把水倒入盆中，把別人的頭摁入水中，可令人窒息死亡。車上有兩樽紅酒，用酒樽扑頭，重則可令傷者成植物人。車上有一樽漂白水，絕對可以令人致傷、致殘，甚至在極度痛楚中死亡。車上有一條耳機線，若用它來繞住一個人的脖頸用力拉緊，後者當然會被勒頸死亡。因此，水、紅酒、漂白水、耳機線統統是攻擊性武器。上了法庭，裁判官會說，「以18個月作量刑起點，沒有任何減刑因素。」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。世上還有清白的人嗎？"},{"pid":"7041eb1aa02c8e3a721eaecb53ab7108ee0278d1","tid":2137886,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8db45c4